The hair dryer market has been experiencing significant growth in recent years due to the increasing focus on personal grooming and styling. Advancements in technology, such as the development of ionic and ceramic hair dryers, have also contributed to the market expansion. Additionally, the rise in disposable income and changing lifestyle preferences have further boosted the demand for hair dryers globally. The market is primarily driven by the beauty and cosmetics industry, where hair dryers are essential tools for both professional salons and personal use.

